# Retro 90s Style Guide

## Color Palette

Classic IBM/DOS theme (use inline styles or CSS variables):

- **Navy Blue**: `#000080` - Base background
- **White**: `#FFFFFF` - Headers, primary headlines
- **Light Gray**: `#AAAAAA` - Body text, secondary content
- **Cyan**: `#00AAAA` - Links, interactive elements
- **Bright Yellow**: `#FFFF55` - Buttons, call-to-actions
- **Lime Green**: `#55FF55` - Highlights, success states

## Typography

```html
<!-- Headlines: Bold, monospace font -->
<h1 class="font-mono text-4xl font-bold" style="color: #FFFFFF;">Welcome!</h1>

<!-- Body text: Monospace/Courier -->
<p class="font-mono text-lg" style="color: #AAAAAA;">Content here...</p>

<!-- Links: Cyan -->
<a href="#" class="font-mono" style="color: #00AAAA;">Click here</a>

<!-- Buttons: Yellow background -->
<button class="font-mono font-bold" style="background: #FFFF55; color: #000080;">READ MORE</button>
```

