## Background Patterns

Classic DOS solid color or subtle patterns:

```html
<body style="background-color: #000080;">
<!-- OR with subtle texture -->
<body class="bg-[#000080]">
```

## Animated Elements

- jQuery effects: `.fadeIn()`, `.slideDown()`, `.animate()`
- CSS animations for blinking text (use sparingly)
- Cursor sparkle trail
- Rainbow text animations using color palette

